<view class="pg">
  <view wx:if="{{list.length}}" class="demobar">演示数据 · 正式版由站内消息表返回</view>
  <block wx:if="{{list.length}}">
    <view class="li" wx:for="{{list}}" wx:key="id">
      <view class="dot {{item.type}}"></view>
      <view class="mi">
        <view class="mt">{{item.title}}</view>
        <view class="mm">{{item.label}} · {{item.time}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>
  <view wx:else class="empty">
    <view class="et">暂无消息</view>
    <view class="ed">预约提醒、补甲回访、优惠券到账、储值召回等,都会记录在这里,方便你随时查看。</view>
  </view>
  <view class="note">这里是站内记录;要在微信里收到锁屏/服务通知提醒,需小程序上线后开通「订阅消息」并授权。</view>
</view>
